title: Alex.Jones.Show.2008.06.23-chakra71
description:
Monday, June 23, 2008

Alex discusses the latest revelations by Barry Jennings on WTC 7. Guests include preeminent occult and secret society researcher Jordan Maxwell and activist Mark Dice who received a death threat from neocon talk show host Michael Reagan. 

Four hours before commercial edit takes it down to 3 hours of playing time.

Note from uploader:  Alex was all over his breaks today.  It's not a problem with the edit, he just never stopped for most of the breaks.  Also the stream did not include the overdrive hour, sorry!  I guess you'll have to sign up at prisonplanet.tv to get it!  ;)
